# Runtime artifacts produced by /eb5-vet and /eb5-compare (keep examples/ checked in)
/findings.json
/*-eb5-report.html
/eb5-report.html
/eb5-compare.html
/*.findings.json

# Runtime artifacts produced by /eb5-prepare and /eb5-gapcheck. These are user
# document packages (may contain personal identity / source-of-funds material) and
# their readiness reports — never commit them if the tool was run inside this repo.
/EB5-Package*/
/_eb5_manifest.json
/EB5-Readiness-Report.md

# Local data files.
# rc_data.json (neutral USCIS name / state / RC-ID snapshot) IS checked in.
# website_results.json is user-supplied (it carries scraped ratings/reviews and
# editorial details about named companies) and is intentionally NOT committed.
/website_results.json
# rc_data.local.json is the runtime self-healing overlay (RCs resolved from the live
# USCIS list by uscis-rc-resolver + rc_append.ps1). Machine-local cache, not committed.
/rc_data.local.json

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
